<br>
For Example : <br>
<br>
/disc Conscentration <br>
Duration : 3 minutes<br>
Recycle time : 30 minutes<br>
Effect : You have a greater chance of landing your spells on any creature, but you have a greater chance of spells landing on you.<br>
<br>
Or something like<br>
<br>
/disc Rapture<br>
Duration : 12 Seconds<br>
Recycle time : 60 minutes<br>
Effect : Any Spell you cast will not be resisted by any creature.<br>
<br>
<br>
Other suggestions would be<br>
<br>
1./disc Suggestion #1<br>
 Duration : 15 Seconds <br>
 Recycle Time : 60 minutes<br>
 Effect : Any spell you cast will not use mana<br>
<br>
<br>
2. /disc Suggestion #2<br>
  Duration : 3 minutes<br>
  Recycle Time : 45 minutes<br>
  Effect : You mana regen's at a rapidly increased rate - This regen stacks with all other regen in the game.<br>
<br>
Also the discs for landing spells would be for int casters, and other discs would be more for wis casters<br>
<br>
For Example<br>
<br>
/disc Suggestion #3<br>
   Duration : Instant<br>
   Recycle Time : 30 minutes<br>
   Effect : The next spell you cast will effect the Entire group, as opposed to a single person.<br>
<br>
Jugernaut<br>
lvl 56 Myrmidon<br>
<br>
